005300     "XXXXX024"                                                   IX1124.2
005400     ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED                                      IX1124.2
005500     ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL                                    IX1124.2
005600     RECORD KEY IS IX-VS2-KEY                                     IX1124.2
005700     FILE STATUS IS IX-VS2-STATUS.                                IX1124.2
