062300 SEQ-INIT-010.                                                    IX1144.2
062400     MOVE ZERO TO TEST-NO.                                        IX1144.2
062500     MOVE "IX-FS3" TO XFILE-NAME (1).                             IX1144.2
062600     MOVE "R1-F-G" TO XRECORD-NAME (1).                           IX1144.2
