031300     MOVE    ZERO TO REC-SKL-SUB.                                 IX2014.2
031400     PERFORM CCVS-INIT-FILE 9 TIMES.                              IX2014.2
031500 CCVS-INIT-FILE.                                                  IX2014.2
031600     ADD     1 TO REC-SKL-SUB.                                    IX2014.2
