000400****************************************************************  IX2064.2
000500*                                                              *  IX2064.2
000600*    VALIDATION FOR:-                                          *  IX2064.2
000700*                                                              *  IX2064.2
000800*    "ON-SITE VALIDATION, NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF STD & TECH.     ".IX2064.2
000900*                                                              *  IX2064.2
