087400     MOVE    "RECORD 182 RETRIEVED"  TO CORRECT-A.                IX2114.2
087500     MOVE "SEQUENTIAL READ; IX-28 4.5.2"  TO RE-MARK.             IX2114.2
087600 READ-WRITE-F1-02.                                                IX2114.2
