111300     PERFORM PRINT-DETAIL.                                        IX2114.2
111400 DISPLAY-ALTERNATE-KEY2.                                          IX2114.2
111500     MOVE    ALTERNATE-KEY2 (1) TO WRK-FD1-ALTKEY2.               IX2114.2
111600     MOVE    FD1-ALTKEY2-1-20  TO COMPUTED-A.                     IX2114.2
