017100*            FROM THE START IN INX-TEST-005.01 THRU               IX2144.2
017200*            INX-TEST-005.09.                                     IX2144.2
017300*      MULTIPLE STARTS. (INX-TEST-007) -  THIS TEST EXECUTES      IX2144.2
